snippet.title: Snacko Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Snacko is now live on Kickstarter!
✨ Check out the campaign: https://bit.ly/snackoks
🎮 Wishlist us on Steam: https://bit.ly/2L8bvTY

📰 Read more about this on our blog: https://bit.ly/2A7SP4y

🐾 About Snacko 🐾
Former big city kitties Momo and Mikan are starting a new life on a seemingly deserted island. Unravel its mysteries while you rebuild a community, farm, fish, and explore the island and beyond!

📌 Website: http://snacko.land
📌 Discord: http://discord.gg/snackodev
📌 Twitter: https://twitter.com/snackodev
